  "texts": [
    "This implies that ChatGPT can not only accurately identify and analyze moral conflicts faced by humans in complex situations, but also comprehensively consider conflicting moral norms and make appropriate choices, demonstrating considerable potential for moral competence.",
    "Upon synthesizing the results of the two-stage experiment, we observed that the moral competence of the GPT series has evolved.",
    "The experimental results demonstrate continuous improvement in the moral judgment competence of LLMs from GPT-2 to GPT-3, culminating in ChatGPT.",
    "This is evident in the \"correctness of moral judgment,\" the \"sufficiency of judgment reasons,\" and the \"logical consistency of judgment reasons.\"",
    "The moral judgments of LLMs are increasingly aligned with human values, with their reasons becoming more refined and logically consistent."
